OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Frather cloudy overnight, but there
OL,7,Fwill be some breaks in the cloud here
OL,8,Fand there. Some patchy rain or drizzle
OL,9,Fpossible, especially over higher
OL,10,Fground, with a little mist and fog
OL,11,Falso forming.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA cloudy start for many with
OL,14,Fpatchy drizzle, mostly in the east.
OL,15,FHowever the cloud will lift and break
OL,16,Fup readily with sunny spells
OL,17,Fdeveloping. Turning wet and windy
OL,18,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
